storyInfo: Saga, the wandering monk, displays her incredible prowess, including the ability to comprehend the Ink Spirits. Confused as she is, Lava goes with Saga to clear the field, arriving at a calm pawn shop.

attributes.content: Is there anyone still left here? Hurry over to the storyteller's and hide!
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: To the east, hurry!
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: Ever since we noticed the sky, I've been conscious of how the further west you go, the more nighttime it actually gets...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: If so, are we currently heading 'from the noon to the twilight?' Quite a poetic ring, actually.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: It's not right. The distance 'from daytime to nighttime' is just too short. We've only gone how far?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: The length of the painting's scroll does vary, and its every sight is a strange, wonderful turn. The people in the picture have all set customs for their world, but in the end, it is still artificial. That much is unavoidable.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: And I'm saying—wait, what?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: What did you just s—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Gyaaaaghh—!
—! Someone's still here?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: This way!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: S—Save me!
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: Fear not, I am here!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkhaa—
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Ho, just as expected. Once cut down, it becomes an ink stain. Most strange, most strange.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Master, I commend your talent!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Lower not your guard, good girl, and make haste for the east!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Got it! You all be careful too!
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: It looks like quite a few villagers didn't run in time.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It was likely too sudden, no chance to—
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Papa? Mama?
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: Th—There's a child there!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Oh no—get down, now!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: She won't make it!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Uwaahhh... waaaaaahh...
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: Ahh!
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: Whoa, there, too close for comfort!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Are you okay?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Uwaaahhh... yeah... uwahhh...
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: Just... just now, did something stab that creature in the throat...?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: That would be Kroos. What a tricky angle.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Where—Where is she?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Don't look, you won't find her. As long as we know she's here, that's good enough. Gotta prioritize ensuring every villager makes it out of the night.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ho, quite the profound rapport. My horizons do broaden.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Wahhh... uwh-uwaah...
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: B—But how do we bring this young girl with us?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You take her out of here, and to somewhere safe. Okay?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Verily! As if I couldn't!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: However—I really cannot bear to cast off my benefactors and take refuge alone! The fact I cannot accompany my benefactors in lopping off heads and spilling fresh blood is a true shame—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You can take the child to Mr. Umbrella's place first and then come back to us.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ahahah... ah... alright, very well now. Very well.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Young miss, would you care to come with me?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: *Sob*... *whimper*... mister, have you seen my mama...? *whimper*...
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: I'll take you to find her, okay?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hic... mm-hm... thank you, mister...
attributes.name: Little Girl

attributes.content: Ahem. Benefactor, shall I depart for now then?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Sir, will we be safe, relying on just Saga and the three heroes?
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: Sir...?
attributes.name: Villager

attributes.content: No matter.
attributes.name: Storyteller

attributes.content: What's wrong with him? Is he in a bad mood today? Did he forget to sleep last night?
attributes.name: Villager A

attributes.content: Sir has culture and grace. He's not the temperamental kind.
attributes.name: Villager B

attributes.content: I bet he's tired, worrying all about us. We should give him some space, let him sleep.
attributes.name: Villager A

attributes.content: Cleanse the six senses!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkhaa!
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Sever all desires!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkhaa!
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Aburaage!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkh... gkhaa?
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: You're pretty strong yourself.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I grew from childhood in the monastery. It influenced me, and I learned a few ways of the sword. That is all.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: You call that a few?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mind not. Stay while I open a path for thee, Lava!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkh... gkhaa!
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Those monsters are starting to fear you... now that I mention it, do Ink Spirits even have intelligence?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Gkh! Gkhaa! Gkhaakh ghkaa!
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Ho?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Why'd you stop?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Gkh, gkh-gkhaa, gkhaahgkhaa...
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Hm, hm-hm, hm...
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Wait?! You can understand what it's saying?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: A bare perception. If thou wouldst observe, this Ink Spirit has not committed any wrongdoing, as if it sincerely regrets, and it will no longer torment the village. We shall let it go, then.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkhaa!
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Is that okay?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It is alright. I know it to be proper.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkh...
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: It's fallen quiet now... There shouldn't be any other villagers remaining. Can we have a chat for a moment?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava, thou art indeed solemn. Perhaps I have done wrong in some way?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: No, you're fine, it's just what you said before... a painting scroll? It seems like you understand this place.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Indeed. I am a wanderer, and have been so for some time.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: This place doesn't seem to deserve the word 'wandering.'
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: How large can a single scroll be?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: What do you mean... are we in a picture?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That is so.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: What exactly do you mean?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ah, I understand now. Your party is akin to me, having erred and fallen into these mountains and rivers—
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: At the outset, I was only passing through the Kou-wu boundary in Yen. Suddenly, I had the thought that I wanted to visit the posterity of the great artist.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: The sight under the waterfalls of Mount Hui-ch'i is beautiful beyond comprehension, and I slept one night in a thatched cottage in the mountains. I had never thought that next I opened my eyes, I would be here.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Hold on, wait. Wait. What do you mean? You were looking for 'Dusk' too?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Dusk? I have never heard tell of this name before...
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: The one I sought was the Yen painter for whom 'one stroke crude mounts rose, whence the words, winds, flow.'
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: But working out the days, I feared that painter had already left our world of mortals, and thus thought to call upon their former residence. That is all.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: In any case, first you went to Mount Hui-ch'i in Kou-wu in Yen, and then you inexplicably ended up here, right?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ho, that is not false, but why does it agitate thee so?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: And then you said this place is a painting scroll—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Nothing of this world conforms to reason. Lava, didst thou never realize?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: No, I know that. But why a painting...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It is difficult to explain, but I have traveled this P'o-shan Village across... about a hundred or more scrolls now! At least, I am well aware of where I myself am.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Guh... those people are real, living people, the tea has flavor, the fruit is edible...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Is this all just some sort of Arts? But if it was... then what kind of...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It is completely beyond my reckoning. Had I not the fortune to glimpse the truth of this world, I fear that I too would be unable to realize where I am.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: No Catastrophe disturbs here, and all living beings follow their own customs, creating their own enclosure, too wondrous for words. Staying here, I have never wanted for ease.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: That's...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hah-hah, the look on thine face is all too unavoidable. When I first met that dusken Hsi-o, she took the same look as thee...
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Slow down... who did you say you met?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I met a—wait now. Those lights, could they be the merchant's shop? So she never took refuge! We must act!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Wait for me!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Gkhaa...
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Alright, alright. Don't get so excited.
attributes.name: Shopkeeper

attributes.content: Why did you come scare the people? What did she tell you?
attributes.name: Shopkeeper

attributes.content: Ah... I see... she's still the same as ever.
attributes.name: Shopkeeper

attributes.content: Shopkeep!
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Gkh...
attributes.name: Ink Spirit

attributes.content: Shopkeep, be thou well?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: I'm fine... And who is this?
attributes.name: Shopkeeper

attributes.content: Oh, this good person is Lava, one of the outsiders who were all the hubbub earlier.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Nice to meet you.
attributes.name: Shopkeeper

attributes.content: This is the proprietor of this shop. Her sole name is 'Dawn,' as of the daybreak.
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: You didn't get attacked by any weird things?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'm not aware of any such things.
attributes.name: Dawn

attributes.content: Young Dawn, I do not know if those Ink Spirits may return again. Wouldst thou permit us to lie in hiding here, to observe for a bare while?
attributes.name: Saga

attributes.content: Mm-hm. Alright.
attributes.name: Dawn
